Ensure you have a local wifi access point (1)
Ensure a passphrase or key is needed to associate with your access point (2)
<dl>
    <dt>Tap the network manager indicator in the upper right-hand corner</dt>
        <dd>you should see it in the list (1)</dd>
    <dt>Tap your wifi access point to connect to it</dt>
        <dd>you will need to enter it now (2)</dd>
    <dt>Wait for the network manager indicator animation to stop</dt>
	<dt>show a successful connection</dt>
    <dt>Tap the icon for Firefox in the launcher</dt>
		<dd>[FILL VERIFICATION]</dd>
    <dt>Browse to some web pages (ex. http://www.ubuntu.com)</dt>
        <dd>The webpages should all load properly</dd>
</dl>
